description: This spiced roasted pumpkin makes a delicious vegetarian entree or side dish with creamy feta and sweet pomegranate.
name: Spiced Roasted Pumpkin & Feta Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Divide the pumpkin wedges between 4 plates, scatter with pumpkin seeds, feta and pomegranate seeds, drizzle over pomegranate molasses and serve.
